::Prowl/Killer/Striker/Ramulus::

Killer growls as he and Prowl go pummeling down to the rocks below, each bot 
trying to get on top.

"Prepare to die, maximal!" Killer says through clenched teeth, forcing Prowl 
under him, the ground approaching at an allarming speed. Suddenly, Prowl 
spins around, kicking his legs out and sending Killer flying down, the 
predacon waving his hands helplessly as he tries to grab on to him.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Striker grunts as the missile blows him into the side of the Ark, nearly 
severing his lower body. His jetpack nearly gives out, but keeps supporting 
him up as he flies up, throwing a grenade down at Hades.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus nods. "Follow me, Longhunter," he says, transforming into beast mode 
and setting off for the Ark at a gallop.
